  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "CMMG Mk47 Mutant 7.62x39 突击步枪",
      "en": "CMMG Mk47 Mutant 7.62x39 assault rifle"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "Mk47",
      "en": "Mk47"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "美国CMMG公司制造的7.62x39毫米口径Mk47 Mutant步枪。它兼容所有种类的AK弹匣，包括钢制弹匣、聚合物弹匣和弹鼓。这把步枪展现出了优越的可靠性，同时拥有AR系统的人体工程学设计，是枪械家族的杰出榜样。这款步枪属于全自动型号，仅供执法单位与军队使用。",
      "en": "CMMG Mk47 Mutant, an American-made carbine chambered in 7.62x39mm, manufactured by CMMG Inc. Works with all types of AK magazines, including steel, polymer and drums. The carbine has shown exceptional reliability, which, together with the classic ergonomics of the AR system, gives an excellent example of a firearm. This variant features a fully automatic firing mode, for Law Enforcement and Millitary use only."
    },
